# --- Raw archival sources (inputs to scripts/build_documents.py) ---
# Pages only serves the generated copies under documents/, so these
# original folders don't need to ship with the site. They remain on
# disk locally for re-running the build script.
Diplomasi belgeleri/
Mahkeme belgeleri/

# --- Historical map sources (raw, input to scripts/process_historical_map.py) ---
# Pages only serves the optimized output at static/maps/, so the raw
# David Rumsey scans don't need to ship with the site.
11517024.jpg
11517024.txt
*.jp2

# NOTE:
# Generated outputs in documents/diplomatic/, documents/judicial/, and
# data/*_documents.{json,js} are intentionally tracked so GitHub Pages
# can serve them without a build step.
